        <div class="post xfolkentry">
         <h1>
          <a class="postheader taggedlink" href="/post/Robbers-in-UKs-Biggest-Jewel-Heist-Sentenced-to-71-Years-in-Prison.aspx">
           Robbers in UK's Biggest Jewel Heist Sentenced to 71 Years in Prison
          </a>
         </h1>
         <div class="descr">
          Monday, 9 August 2010 10:13 by
          <a href="/author/Roe Kalb.aspx">
           Roe Kalb
          </a>
         </div>
         <div class="entry" style="direction:ltr;">
          <p>
           The four robbers who stole 40 million worth of jewels from
           <a href="/post/Londons-Latest-Sting-Innovative-Jewelry-Stealing-Techniques.aspx" rel="Diamonds, Robbery, Graff, London" target="_blank" title="Diamond Robbery">
            Mayfair's Graff Diamonds
           </a>
           last summer have been sentenced to a total of 71 years in prison, The Daily Star reports.
          </p>
          <p>
           The ringleader of the biggest jewel heist in UK history, Aman Kassaye, and his accomplices  Solomun Beyene, Clinton Mogg, and Thomas Thomas  held the Graff Diamonds staff at gunpoint while forcing employee Petra Ehnar to empty the display cases.
          </p>
          <p>
           Kassaye then forced Ehnar out of the store and onto the street at gunpoint, eventually making his getaway in a series of cars.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           Forty-three pieces of jewelry  including one
           <a href="http://www.israelidiamond.co.il/english" rel="Diamonds, Diamond" target="_blank" title="Diamond">
            diamond
           </a>
           necklace valued at 3.5 million  were taken during the robbery. The jewels have yet to be found or returned.
          </p>
          <p>
           Although Kassaye had hired a professional makeup artist to disguise his appearance, Ehnar identified him. Kassaye, for his part, argued that someone else  bearing a striking resemblance to him  had been responsible for the robbery.
          </p>
          <p>
           Kassaye was sentenced to 23 years in prison  16 for conspiracy to rob, five years for being in possession of a firearm, and two years for kidnap. Each of the other three men was sentenced to 16 years on the charge of conspiracy to rob.
          </p>
          <p>
           <span class="Apple-style-span" style="font: normal normal normal medium/normal 'Times New Roman'; border-collapse: separate; -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px">
            <span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 13px; color: #444444; line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">
             <strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px">

                <span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 12px; color: #666666; line-height: 17px; font-family: Arial; padding: 0px; margin: 0px">
                 <strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px">
